attributes.title: Barenaked Ladies - "Did I Say That Out Loud?" (Official Music Video)
attributes.description:
New recordings available on iTunes at http://Smarturl.it/BNLJuly1

Barenaked Ladies recently digitally released The Long Weekend EP in Canada & a deluxe bonus edition of 'Grinning Streak' in the US! Both feature previously unreleased recordings plus acoustic renditions of select album tracks. BNL head back to the States on their cross country summer tour starting July 17th in Stamford,Ct and wraping up on September 14th. Special VIP tour packages are available. For more information on VIP Packages and tour dates visit http://www.barenakedladies.com.
